commit.message:
Make prvect tail recursive (fix #9355)

Using a unit test as it's way faster than messing with universes.

You can test with universes by
~~~coq
Set Universe Polymorphism.
Definition x1@{i} := True.
Definition x2 := x1 -> x1.
Definition x3 := x2 -> x2.
Definition x4 := x3 -> x3.
Definition x5 := x4 -> x4.
Definition x6 := x5 -> x5.

Definition x8 := x7 -> x7.
Definition x9 := x8 -> x8.
